Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • player.Player
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Computer, Human

    public class Player
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains everything a player owns (name, team/color, buildings, cards, points). Superclass of Human and Computer.
